On just another little different tangent, the 
1986 Immigration Act, where they gave amnesty to

28:23.917 --> 28:41.256
the illegal residents of over eight years, has 
that had any impact on protecting our borders? No,

28:42.097 --> 28:45.741
I don't think so. The immigration situation is 
different from the drug situation. It's not to say

28:54.190 --> 28:59.155
that some of these people maybe won't carry small 
amounts in, or even large amounts. We don't know.

29:01.078 --> 29:23.522
But I think what the amnesty program has probably

29:01.078 --> 29:23.522
brought more and more people from Mexico, 
interior, and even more than that from Central

29:01.078 --> 29:23.522
America, into this area, looking for ways to do 
that. I don't think it affects customs, per se,

29:29.664 --> 29:35.631
that much. Okay, and two final questions. First of 
all, are we winning the war? And if not, what would

29:40.677 --> 29:45.643
it take to

29:40.677 --> 29:45.643
win? We're clearly not winning the

29:45.663 --> 29:51.990
war. As I say, I've been involved in this war, 
so-called war, since the Nixon administration,

29:53.135 --> 30:03.549
and it's only gotten worse every year since 1973. 
Every year is worse than the year before. The only

30:07.595 --> 30:18.450
way to win the war, in my mind, is a 
multi-directional

30:07.595 --> 30:18.450
kind of an effort. But the most important thing is 
we've got to stop the demand for it. I don't know how

30:26.628 --> 30:30.113
to do that. I don't know whether it means we have to 
arrest people who use it.

30:38.666 --> 30:47.039
We certainly need education, prevention, 
treatment, decriminalization maybe. I don't

30:47.059 --> 30:47.560
know. I don't know what the answer is. All I know is 
that there's always going to be an element in this

30:50.445 --> 31:00.779
society that appears to want to do the illegal 
drugs. Maybe only because they're illegal.

31:04.243 --> 31:10.372
They're always going to want to turn their friends 
on to

31:04.243 --> 31:10.372
it. Everybody knows crack is dangerous. But 
you've got a million kids who want to do it. I don't

31:16.940 --> 31:17.361
know why. You've got to get rid of the demand. As 
long as there's a demand, there are going to be

